data.description: Welcome home to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath ranch home with covered front porch and rear deck on 2 private acres.  Freshly painted and ready for new owner!  Spacious kitchen with brand new floor, stainless steel appliances; formal dining room with hardwood floors; living room with pastoral views; 3 bedrooms on main level including primary bedroom with ensuite bath with brand new floor; hall bath has been totally renovated; basement is partially finished with large family room with fireplace; roof and heat pump were recently replaced, large private backyard; No HOA. 30 minutes to Charlottesville.
